@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mauyki(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v2 - 0.68)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.44)) + ((tmp + 0.92 - tmp + 0.27) * 0.47))
    v2 = v0
    v1 = 0.65
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.83 * v0 + 0.02)))
    v1 = (0.20 + wp.abs((v0 + 0.95 / tmp + 0.20)))
    tmp = 0.71
    data[tid] = v0
